# RASCAL - Complete Setup Guide

## 🚀 Quick Start Overview

This guide will take you from unboxed components to a fully functional autonomous delivery robot.

**Total Setup Time:** 8-10 hours (first build)  
**Difficulty Level:** Intermediate  
**Required Skills:** Basic soldering, Arduino programming, hardware assembly

---

## 📦 Before You Begin

### Tools Checklist
- [ ] Soldering iron and solder
- [ ] Wire stripper/cutter
- [ ] Multimeter
- [ ] Screwdriver set (Phillips #1, #2)
- [ ] Hot glue gun (optional)
- [ ] Helping hands/PCB holder
- [ ] Safety glasses

### Software Requirements
- [ ] Arduino IDE 1.8.19 or 2.x
- [ ] USB Type-B cable (for Arduino Mega)
